{"title":"Fibrinolisis en IM","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Fibrinolisis en IM-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Fibrinolisis","guid":"C7ChPlgEpzAe_TyyimmQ3w","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Terapia fibrinolítica:","guid":"Y2mOwrB1qbtgvxgmNY0qAw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Mecanismo de\\Nacción:","guid":"ugYKwQYQQp7tJBKlUBhSZw","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"⬆ Concentración de plasmina → corte de trombina y fibrina (n5).","guid":"a5P1QKoxMTfsSeqZ5yz_-A","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"⬆ Degradación de trombos (activan plasminógeno → plasmina)","guid":"G7PRh5Ra1rw6lWVvbVCOxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Agentes\\Nfibrinolíticos","guid":"Iz2xVrLd1BRPnXZ-FZZ2Yg","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"a. Agentes específicos\\Nde fibrina:","guid":"NcrBCisSOx7y0743UQtVlA","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• tPA (activador tisular de plasminógeno)","guid":"vSrQRf-PRWkGPvrc0y7rQg","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• rtPA (activadores recombinantes\\Nde plasminógeno):","guid":"FfPHdLwlkvi7VO0QxEx5wQ","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Alteplase","guid":"2ld-1siLesVrSBMKHbwYeg","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"Reteplase (rPA)","guid":"o-837TY1xhxxzByNhWM53w","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"Tenecteplase (TNK-tPA)","guid":"c6LA4fSUrrjWbb3GiHDLiQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"5","text":"b. Agentes no\\Nespecíficos de fibrina:","guid":"wmD95z2zDYwM7zCz830yOQ","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• Estreptoquinasa (enzima de estreptococos grupo A, cataliza plasminógeno → plasmina)","guid":"3ZqRhxh_BRSeEVQBtjg9TA","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"• Uroquinasa (proteasa serina en plasma, orina, tejidos)","guid":"w8-d2O_XY4ulh-v57X5cbw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"1","text":"Hallazgos de\\Nlaboratorio:","guid":"aXwllrUL-16o8RWOPMWmaA","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• ↑ PT","guid":"Jy315TMfaRfUXRkye_mgfw","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"• ↑ PTT","guid":"gTSOgehOviJPT2_zezkm6w","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"• Plaquetas normales","guid":"I_SFVaAgX_EDt96uhqQXMA","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"1","text":"Efectos\\Nadversos:","guid":"LnVf3qW_DOTNKeAgEP8BSw","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Sangrado (ej. hemorragia intracraneal)","guid":"Vf23qdHDTyUB9zabwOTV5Q","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"• Reacciones de hipersensibilidad (estreptoquinasa)","guid":"a2F7HRqiMHLlMKXbcNg2Ng","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"1","text":"Indicaciones:","guid":"kgYhlQbQcFYg2fh7hAaU5g","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• IAM c/ elevación del ST (STEMI)","guid":"7DITJAiXRc8ztZ9dP7v3aw","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"• ACV isquémico","guid":"KVkGCsPzE0l7-bXjNaK0vw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"• Embolia pulmonar masiva","guid":"wMnFiLQx9TsAPn8NdT1KIA","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"1","text":"Contraindicaciones:","guid":"c_uk4u56hV7IUIgU--jNsg","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Sangrado activo","guid":"qVHBkIPHr_YMbmjNdgyFKg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Hemorragia intracraneal previa","guid":"UZ99VZd7dsYQOfpgkkN8bg","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• Cirugía reciente","guid":"U6lQIrmyAdlmbtU_uJyuRg","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"• Hipertensión grave","guid":"Yeo_z4XJyPt7OWxQY__EFw","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"• Diátesis hemorrágica conocida","guid":"S8BkAuOa2uuwEzo2XTonsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"1","text":"Reversión de\\Nefectos adversos:","guid":"SJbC5wTsGQgRN2m1efKHwg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Ácido tranexámico (análogo sintético de lisina, inhibe plasminógeno)","guid":"2jDhiqK9F1_murKeMq3rxA","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Ácido aminocaproico (derivado de lisina, inhibe activadores de plasminógeno y plasmina)","guid":"p6p0sqxr2fISrFg9zTrJmQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"• Plasma fresco congelado (PFC), concentrado de complejo protrombínico (CCP)\\No crioprecipitado (⬆ factor VIII y fibrinógeno que PFC)","guid":"3TGsCvbSUa4-1hhRDFE4Ng","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"• Transfusiones de plaquetas (si es necesario)","guid":"Muicx3wT7PQgDfVGlqdcug","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"1","text":"Alteplase: Activador tisular sintético de plasminógeno, convierte plasminógeno\\N→ plasmina. Uso en: STEMI, embolia pulmonar masiva, ACV isquémico.","guid":"Oerg-Nar6H_qCQHAuAh1Sg","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"0","text":"Indicaciones (en STEMI y equivalentes de\\NSTEMI, si se cumplen todas):","guid":"F463lbgRFUXMs_P3A0cUMA","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• No se puede realizar PCI en ≤ 120 min después de FMC","guid":"reKzVhxZiWLmnBfvaXbGxg","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"• Inicio de síntomas:","guid":"IrObKLaK7PYNd7rn2ZgcNg","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"≤ 12 hrs","guid":"5oBm3W3i_XslhmqMiePVvQ","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"12-24 hrs con signos clínicos de isquemia continua\\N(PCI preferible en este contexto)","guid":"DxjrqqXipO2tSIrYnnKeOA","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"38","text":"• No hay contraind. a fibrinólisis","guid":"xOufEzoHDlHPPc8w7AMRJg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"38","text":"• ⏱ Tiempo: dentro de < 30 min tras llegada al hospital (n2)","guid":"V8OSlR_uE5AS5SfaR6Mtzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"Contraindicaciones:","guid":"BulhgztUCEnb86fstjmnxQ","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• Si > 24 hrs desde inicio de síntomas","guid":"808H6CeYX7Gyw_F0m2HE_A","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"Contraindicaciones comunes para\\Nfibrinólisis en STEMI y equivalentes:","guid":"JHnZ50PDPnMc9ZoKREGgOw","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"a. Absolutas:","guid":"Zw8hatMJh5BFQBuEz8zUAQ","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Sangrado activo (excluyendo menstruación)","guid":"WCQu-KhlwRA5bSGl3GM3ZA","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"• Diátesis hemorrágica/conocida coagulopatía","guid":"W-xQJTjjB9CpFxnF5B2MBA","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"• Hemorragia intracraneal previa","guid":"nx7MZxLt8N69ZQ5WafmcpQ","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"• Cirugía intracraneal/intraespinal en últimos 2 meses","guid":"e_uwM5m4w9gkLbc986KahQ","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"48","text":"• Trauma grave en cabeza en últimos 3 meses","guid":"QmZpCG0U6PPqSgcIgbTA9Q","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"48","text":"• ACV isquémico en últimos 3 meses","guid":"hPWqNAozc4351ZlUCNKvVg","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"48","text":"• HTA severa no responsiva a tto. de emergencia","guid":"CgVg0aVOq22HppX012Nmag","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"48","text":"• Condiciones intracraneales que ⬆ riesgo de sangrado (ej. malformación arteriovenosa)","guid":"MjqH33OpHCd0INxcm_g0pw","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"48","text":"• Sospecha de disección aórtica","guid":"nXyWFANhxwwmyw6GIYx7LA","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"48","text":"• Malignidad intracraneal","guid":"4cccYiH3uM9R6uM3LB-y1g","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"48","text":"(Para estreptoquinasa:)","guid":"R_4WEG_LvId0J4RVKOHmqA","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Exposición previa en últimos 6 meses (altamente antigénica) (n29, n28)","guid":"xge3UKHZ8OmQ9dFKwwsPgQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"47","text":"b. Relativas:","guid":"EGxctSTIRR94rF9AAIhmKQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Cirugía mayor en últimos 21 días","guid":"rYbYageMDerHk2l0huvRmA","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"• PAS > 180 mm Hg o PAD > 110 mm Hg","guid":"nB4peaheaztV6F0LSCEqeg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"• ACV isquémico > 3 meses atrás","guid":"1BJqISHP6lZiOC3IvWoPBA","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"• Neoplasias sólidas","guid":"RO5dm5atAxDujiBclq3SXQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"61","text":"• Sangrado interno (ej. sangrado GI) en últimas 2-4 semanas","guid":"wf6a6svYXVXB-SgqhpGR3w","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"61","text":"• Tto. con anticoagulantes orales","guid":"7acQDIV8kUtfo7qoYyWTZA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"61","text":"• RCP prolongada o traumática (> 10 min)","guid":"paxZlDPQ7YvtNANPRUXJ7Q","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"61","text":"• Punción en sitio vascular no compresible","guid":"f1u-evbC2Y3Ljg7VUlgUWw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"61","text":"• HTA crónica severa y mal controlada","guid":"W9JYup3q7eIVyJa-_BlSKQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"61","text":"• Anormalidad estructural intracraneal no considerada absoluta contraindicación","guid":"h_eOROXA3qb4NJ4ffzuHqQ","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"61","text":"• Endocarditis infecciosa","guid":"IIz8zDR72yKV3D7lHAJyrw","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"61","text":"• Úlcera péptica activa","guid":"V_wvWf2umHZsiOoO3vHyAg","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"61","text":"• Disfunción hepática significativa","guid":"zHaEzWRXiq_Wv68saA7fLg","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"61","text":"• Embarazo o en 7 días postparto","guid":"h4N1bLqWDdLjVqXDnIEJsQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"61","text":"• Demencia (n28, n8)","guid":"TWNgqE-w7vNSG32oh9flFA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"0","text":"Opciones de terapias\\Nde reperfusión:","guid":"yTIKqZ3M2kX3L7wnY5rMFw","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"Reperfusión\\Nfarmacológica:","guid":"q_pbs2vG_2Mibr1NmtFGIA","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"• Fibrinólisis: Uso de fármacos EV (estreptokinasa, alteplase, reteplase, tenecteplase)\\N→ lisis del coágulo y restablecimiento del flujo coronario.","guid":"YiCP-q5SojXub7WZGq4wGw","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"Mayor eficacia dentro de las primeras 3 horas (menor beneficio posterior).","guid":"ehKijNeBIH31LnFmq8J5Wg","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"⬆ Permeabilidad del vaso ocluido entre 30-50% según trombolítico (n27).","guid":"INEReF1LvqwYKHrHRDFrZA","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"78","text":"FFT: ↓ Mortalidad 30% (1 hr), 25% (2-3 hrs), 18% (4-6 hrs).\\NEvita 30 muertes/1000 pacientes < 6 hrs, y 20 muertes/1000 pacientes entre 7-12 hrs (n28).","guid":"w5w7QMp-DXGw0CvL0oRs6Q","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"78","text":"Fibrinolisis prehospitalaria: ↓ Mortalidad 17% en meta-análisis\\N(16 muertes evitadas/1000 pacientes) (n30).","guid":"4vPnyLlWp9Eng8mvCkz3Ig","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"77","text":"Riesgos de la\\Nfibrinólisis:","guid":"N3v8mmhi-vzS03Kz5kAKiQ","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• Principal riesgo: Hemorragia intracraneal \\N(0.9-1% de pacientes, concentrada en primer día)","guid":"QOuvmrQi8Ky3yvKgI9nolQ","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Predictores: Edad avanzada, bajo peso, sexo femenino,\\NECV previa, HTA al ingreso (n31, n32).","guid":"ZtqvGkDSZpWOmBp8jq-Mjg","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"• Otras hemorragias: No cerebrales (4-13% pacientes tratados)\\N→ pueden requerir transfusión (n33).","guid":"aVV8jaWOadnlLv9YXXFl9Q","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"• Asociado: Arritmias ventriculares → necesario monitoreo. Estreptokinasa puede\\Ncausar hipotensión (resolución con volumen), raras reacciones alérgicas (n35).","guid":"O2yY0Oc29qCMZbqq28IQ3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"77","text":"Reperfusión\\Nmecánica:","guid":"IlncgaqzVMN1goUjidT4dQ","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Angioplastía coronaria percutánea (ACP)","guid":"Icewbn3W8ZvcuOQi9ARp1g","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"• Cirugía de by-pass coronario de urgencia (en casos seleccionados).","guid":"QvNG3FXSZkuFC4jtgLKhMw","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"77","text":"Elección del fármaco\\Nfibrinolítico:","guid":"gJj-54sh8iwItThMMJzegA","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"• Alteplase (régimen acelerado): Infusión en 90 min.","guid":"2uMj4iQokrIKr_Cbm3KaNA","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"• Estreptokinasa (SK): Infusión IV 30-60 min → ⬆ riesgo de hipotensión (n37).","guid":"ivJKxd6S03382onn2XMNkA","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"• Reteplase (r-PA): Administración en bolo.","guid":"EJkTywhWZB_Se2ZNROg83w","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"92","text":"• Tenecteplase (TNK): Bolo, ⬇ riesgo de hemorragia no cerebral\\N(26.4% vs. 28.9%) y necesidad de transfusión (4.2% vs. 5.5%) (n32).","guid":"pQlk5eriTeFasO84j3jdAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"77","text":"• Comparación: Tenecteplase = Alteplase en mortalidad a 30 días,\\Npero menor riesgo de hemorragia no cerebral y transfusión (n32).","guid":"D2KPOANL62wHQNAI9VW21w","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"77","text":"Nota: PCI indicada incluso después de trombólisis exitosa.","guid":"AzP-qEs2Ni5QVN7FrKtomQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"0","text":"Comparación de\\Nfibrinolíticos:","guid":"J1rAoss77XHukGU787SMFQ","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"a. Dosis","guid":"P8mu6T9AOCeGSq1Q31DSHA","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"• Alteplase: Hasta 100 mg en 90 min","guid":"I9N5aCnyMXhuGARa-hUE6A","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"• Estreptokinasa: 1.500. 000 UI en 30-60 min","guid":"NNyhE_-7kDpQbbYAercUgw","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"• Reteplase: 30-50 mg (según peso)","guid":"sMuipkYB8aji4XWi7ivZpg","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"100","text":"• Tenecteplase: 30-50 mg (según peso)","guid":"dTcS_lrf4-W1IEWQHIFGOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"99","text":"b. Administración","guid":"dl44nzdQ4brw3PHVG1OlMw","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Alteplase: Infusión","guid":"EJ-7WGitCIW_yKb7ER8lwA","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"• Estreptokinasa: Infusión","guid":"4w3d7Osvix5k9ZHdCw6YSw","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"• Reteplase: Bolo","guid":"VSGD7nz2YSNVHbNvQNlxlw","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"• Tenecteplase: Bolo","guid":"L8SzW9hYt9E7FeOS8RlzNw","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"99","text":"c. Antigénico","guid":"uDconPuFc5axYfKEwGzcFw","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"• Estreptokinasa: Sí","guid":"z_FI0Zfrr_H6NfTrs1xmzA","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"• Alteplase, Reteplase, Tenecteplase: No","guid":"OHVLm4Ie7sV80EkyiN2P9Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"99","text":"d. Reacciones\\Nadversas","guid":"g-OqPUGeXJeAINxhsWZC3g","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Estreptokinasa: Hipotensión","guid":"iSzSxlAPRFT-UA2TkeS4WA","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"• Alteplase, Reteplase, Tenecteplase: No","guid":"HmFo6_3OTxXjmIwkOjtrKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"99","text":"e. Flujo TIMI 3 (%)","guid":"yFaDckLbZ3hSer2GjJz1VQ","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"• Alteplase: 54%","guid":"xWCNIP_PTo8BJM5pBokX8w","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"• Estreptokinasa: 60%","guid":"lRC1BaC6BAkIZM7CoCN9sA","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"116","text":"• Reteplase: 63%","guid":"o3OtBFnLd3WoL20NtGtp6Q","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"116","text":"• Tenecteplase: 63%","guid":"p6y5C2gTX8K7l--UmS07ew","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"99","text":"f. Costo","guid":"X2Qd57IHrNZB_4p5nKVwag","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• Alteplase: $ +","guid":"5Okc7qOs-hfoH6zBH2znmQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• Estreptokinasa, Reteplase, Tenecteplase: $ +++","guid":"CoT33938MUo4Sc0WV-Yp_g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación\\NTIMI:","guid":"EcF_RIejKslUFhuCStBgAg","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"• Grado 0 = Sin perfusión","guid":"x9_JVWasp4ZeQqB4Edy4Rg","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"• Grado 1 = Mínima perfusión","guid":"hVthLpOwTmxEL0YdJDqGtg","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"124","text":"• Grado 2 = Perfusión parcial","guid":"zJsg6zAVdvM0Jqvsn_x66w","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"124","text":"• Grado 3 = Perfusión completa","guid":"wdGQDJHV3Au6OsKAb7MaDg","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"0","text":"Criterios de reperfusión\\N(90-120 min post trombólisis):","guid":"LQiMdHq6fDK7shxyHPl2qA","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"• ↓ Dolor","guid":"YpTOUeCdqgV9-Kk7MH-1sQ","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"• ↓ Supradesnivel del ST","guid":"MfhFiB6nU1VfvxazZkYYog","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Valor pronóstico: ↓ ST ≥ 50% (idealmente > 70%) (n40).","guid":"QEEB8YXxsE0F8stzLg9CGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"129","text":"• ⬆ Enzimas miocárdicas","guid":"7JmQToXEAX8Ra1YJIFVZsQ","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"129","text":"• Arritmias de reperfusión","guid":"STZXTIQtLyMxeWH0CqFwAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"0","text":"Tenecteplase\\N(TNK):","guid":"PQsnm0o7lvsrciUpamD8Qg","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"Dosis:","guid":"hx1XnKyTONmUfDXbpSCLmw","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"<60 kg: 30 mg i.v.","guid":"rbeJQQWWvVW4_o2mxkbkEA","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"60-<70 kg: 35 mg i.v.","guid":"PrCz7NDoi710lG9TelhavQ","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"70-<80 kg: 40 mg i.v.","guid":"lQohrW3tE_3kOZXfFqgjUA","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"136","text":"80-<90 kg: 45 mg i.v.","guid":"06xbyXr-TAq7UwtwbZKZRA","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"136","text":"≥90 kg: 50 mg i.v.","guid":"aJrHjYO4c1p2ykP_YqIuGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"135","text":"Terapia antitrombínica:","guid":"8sT_PyGqv5NExXHqx_IjYQ","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"Enoxaparina:","guid":"zzymJtPI3fppl0W2qz_Unw","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"<75 años: 30 mg i.v. + 1 mg/kg s.c. c/12 hrs.","guid":"Hi5K9OqG1ic87X2sCTy28A","children":[]},{"id"